00:03:30.011 --> 00:03:31.378 position:27% line:89% align:start
8 sun in length.

00:03:31.411 --> 00:03:33.014 position:24% line:89% align:start
Shobu-style blades.

00:03:33.047 --> 00:03:34.749 position:19% line:89% align:start
The hilt is consistent.

00:03:34.782 --> 00:03:36.383 position:24% line:89% align:start
Tsumugari-no-Tachi.

00:03:36.416 --> 00:03:39.286 position:16% line:89% align:start
White metallic in color.

00:03:39.319 --> 00:03:40.855 position:27% line:89% align:start
There's no doubt.

00:03:40.888 --> 00:03:42.056 position:35% line:77% align:start
This is --
Karin: Fena!

00:03:42.090 --> 00:03:44.926 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yukimaru! Shitan!

00:03:44.959 --> 00:03:46.060 position:61% line:89% align:start
Hey!

00:03:46.094 --> 00:03:48.129 position:44% line:83% align:start
If you're there,
answer me!

00:03:48.162 --> 00:03:49.564 position:10% line:89% align:start
What's going on?

00:03:49.597 --> 00:03:53.067 position:30% line:5% align:start
Tsubaki: Wait.
Nobody's seen them?

00:03:53.101 --> 00:03:56.170 position:24% line:5% align:start
I can't believe you guys!
Seriously.

00:03:56.204 --> 00:03:57.205 position:52% line:83% align:start
You all saw
treasure

00:03:57.237 --> 00:03:58.405 position:47% line:83% align:start
and completely
dropped the ball.

00:03:58.438 --> 00:04:00.074 position:64% line:83% align:start
Karin: Like
you two can talk!

00:04:00.108 --> 00:04:02.409 position:7% line:83% align:start
Shitan: I last saw them walking
off towards the upper area.

00:04:02.442 --> 00:04:05.345 position:19% line:83% align:start
Same here,
but that was a while ago.

00:04:05.378 --> 00:04:07.181 position:47% line:83% align:start
You mean to say
they've been missing

00:04:07.215 --> 00:04:08.683 position:44% line:89% align:start
ever since then?

00:04:08.716 --> 00:04:11.052 position:24% line:83% align:start
Here's what we do.
We go search that area.

00:04:11.085 --> 00:04:13.054 position:16% line:89% align:start
No need to worry till --

00:04:13.087 --> 00:04:16.256 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Sighs ]

00:04:19.193 --> 00:04:21.229 position:58% line:83% align:start
What's wrong,
Tsubaki?

00:04:21.261 --> 00:04:23.097 position:21% line:89% align:start
Tsubaki?

00:04:23.131 --> 00:04:29.904 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:04:29.937 --> 00:04:33.306 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh!

00:04:33.340 --> 00:04:34.976 position:35% line:89% align:start
This is...

00:04:35.009 --> 00:04:36.244 position:35% line:89% align:start
This is...

00:04:36.276 --> 00:04:39.247 position:16% line:83% align:start
Before you is
The Vault of the Earth.

00:04:39.279 --> 00:04:40.815 position:30% line:89% align:start
The San Miguel.

00:04:40.848 --> 00:04:41.983 position:33% line:89% align:start
Captain Kidd.

00:04:42.016 --> 00:04:43.251 position:35% line:89% align:start
Holy Grail.

00:04:43.283 --> 00:04:44.484 position:21% line:89% align:start
Ark of the Covenant.

00:04:44.519 --> 00:04:46.087 position:21% line:89% align:start
The Knights Templar.

00:04:46.120 --> 00:04:48.256 position:10% line:89% align:start
Treasure of La Noche Triste.

00:04:48.288 --> 00:04:50.525 position:27% line:83% align:start
You will find all
of the world's

00:04:50.558 --> 00:04:53.728 position:19% line:83% align:start
greatest lost treasures
in this place.

00:04:53.761 --> 00:04:55.229 position:24% line:83% align:start
They were gathered
and brought here

00:04:55.263 --> 00:04:56.463 position:16% line:89% align:start
by those with a calling.

00:04:56.496 --> 00:04:58.232 position:16% line:89% align:start
Lying in wait for the day

00:04:58.266 --> 00:05:00.101 position:24% line:83% align:start
they may be of use
to the world.

00:05:00.134 --> 00:05:04.205 position:13% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ] Ooh!

00:05:04.238 --> 00:05:07.275 position:21% line:83% align:start
By jove,
I found it!

00:05:07.307 --> 00:05:08.743 position:35% line:89% align:start
[ Laughs ]

00:05:08.776 --> 00:05:11.212 position:30% line:89% align:start
It's all mine!

00:05:11.245 --> 00:05:13.981 position:35% line:89% align:start
[ Gunshot ]

00:05:14.015 --> 00:05:16.349 position:33% line:89% align:start
[ Men gasp ]

00:05:23.591 --> 00:05:25.626 position:21% line:83% align:start
Let this be a lesson
to you all.

00:05:25.660 --> 00:05:28.830 position:21% line:83% align:start
Those who are blinded
by treasure will be executed.

00:05:28.863 --> 00:05:31.566 position:33% line:89% align:start
[ All gasp ]

00:05:31.599 --> 00:05:33.835 position:16% line:89% align:start
Have I made myself clear?

00:05:33.868 --> 00:05:35.136 position:55% line:89% align:start
Aye, sir!

00:05:35.169 --> 00:05:37.337 position:10% line:77% align:start
Loud and clear!
Men: Aye, sir!

00:05:39.307 --> 00:05:41.943 position:16% line:83% align:start
There's no point hiding,
goblins!

00:05:41.976 --> 00:05:44.846 position:13% line:83% align:start
I know that you're in here,
hiding like cowards!

00:05:44.879 --> 00:05:47.181 position:27% line:83% align:start
Time to come out
with your hands up!

00:05:47.215 --> 00:05:50.284 position:38% line:83% align:start
Do that,
and I will spare your lives!

00:05:50.318 --> 00:05:51.552 position:7% line:89% align:start
What now?

00:05:51.586 --> 00:05:53.154 position:24% line:83% align:start
There's quite a few
of them.

00:05:53.187 --> 00:05:55.590 position:38% line:89% align:start
Tsubaki?

00:05:55.623 --> 00:05:58.059 position:19% line:83% align:start
I think...
Fena and Yukimaru

00:05:58.092 --> 00:06:00.127 position:16% line:83% align:start
probably went
to where we're headed.

00:06:00.161 --> 00:06:02.196 position:5% line:89% align:start
To the final location.

00:06:02.230 --> 00:06:04.165 position:7% line:89% align:start
And if they did...

00:06:04.198 --> 00:06:05.432 position:27% line:89% align:start
If they went on ahead...

00:06:05.465 --> 00:06:08.135 position:44% line:83% align:start
then our role is
to act as their shield.

00:06:08.169 --> 00:06:10.470 position:30% line:83% align:start
It may cost us
our lives.

00:06:10.504 --> 00:06:12.340 position:52% line:83% align:start
Well, then,
so be it.

00:06:12.372 --> 00:06:13.341 position:35% line:89% align:start
Both: Huh?

00:06:13.373 --> 00:06:14.809 position:5% line:89% align:start
[ Chuckles ]

00:06:14.842 --> 00:06:26.320 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:06:26.354 --> 00:06:27.822 position:47% line:89% align:start
No sign of 'em.

00:06:27.855 --> 00:06:30.324 position:10% line:83% align:start
Search every nook
and cranny.

00:06:30.358 --> 00:06:32.827 position:7% line:83% align:start
I know they're here
somewhere.

00:06:32.860 --> 00:06:33.928 position:61% line:89% align:start
