00:11:38.232 --> 00:11:39.200 position:55% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:11:39.233 --> 00:11:49.210 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:11:49.243 --> 00:11:59.153 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:11:59.186 --> 00:12:08.896 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:12:08.929 --> 00:12:12.766 position:19% line:83% align:start
