00:12:27.582 --> 00:12:39.561 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:12:39.594 --> 00:12:41.028 position:47% line:89% align:start
Mm!

00:12:41.061 --> 00:12:44.566 position:38% line:89% align:start
