00:12:44.599 --> 00:12:54.074 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:12:54.108 --> 00:12:56.443 position:33% line:89% align:start
[ Groaning ]

00:13:01.448 --> 00:13:02.584 position:24% line:89% align:start
[ Inhales sharply ]

00:13:02.617 --> 00:13:05.986 position:58% line:89% align:start
I see.

00:13:06.020 --> 00:13:09.691 position:47% line:83% align:start
