from that night.

00:13:09.724 --> 00:13:11.825 position:50% line:89% align:start
How amusing.

00:13:14.795 --> 00:13:15.829 position:5% line:89% align:start
What are you doing?!

00:13:15.863 --> 00:13:17.264 position:21% line:83% align:start
Get back!
No!

00:13:20.134 --> 00:13:22.604 position:52% line:89% align:start
Stay away!

00:13:22.637 --> 00:13:24.471 position:21% line:89% align:start
Helena...

00:13:24.506 --> 00:13:25.507 position:27% line:89% align:start
[ Wind whistles ]

00:13:25.540 --> 00:13:26.840 position:27% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:13:33.380 --> 00:13:34.982 position:44% line:89% align:start
Fena?

00:13:35.015 --> 00:13:36.751 position:24% line:89% align:start
[ Thunder crashes ]

00:13:36.785 --> 00:13:38.185 position:41% line:89% align:start
Fena...

00:13:38.218 --> 00:13:39.987 position:44% line:89% align:start
I won't let you.

00:13:40.020 --> 00:13:43.190 position:5% line:83% align:start
You're not hurting him
ever again!

00:13:43.223 --> 00:13:44.659 position:30% line:89% align:start
It's my turn...

00:13:44.693 --> 00:13:47.227 position:21% line:89% align:start
